            <title>[CAMEL-4695] Calling the camel-smpp component results in a NullPointerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-4695</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the camel-smpp component is called to submit a SMS, a NullPointerException is thrown:&lt;/p&gt;

